        "legal": {
          "label": "Airstrike?",
          "image": "https://dwaugh-edsim.github.io/projectimages/cuba62/airstrike-doc.jpg",
          "credit": "JOINT CHIEFS MEMORANDUM - AI",
          "content": "### MEMORANDUM FOR THE PRESIDENT\n**FROM:** Joint Chiefs of Staff (JCS)\n**SUBJECT:** OPLAN 312 (Air Strike Plan)\n\nThe Military Generals are unanimous: These missiles are a deadly threat. We propose the immediate use of **OPLAN 312**: A massive air attack to blow up the missile sites at sunrise, followed by a full invasion of Cuba (OPLAN 316).\n\n**The Legal Argument:**\nAttorney General Robert Kennedy warns that a surprise airstrike is 'Pearl Harbor in reverse.' He argues it would make the US look like a bully and ruin our reputation for 100 years. However, General Maxwell Taylor argues that the Soviets started it by secretly bringing nuclear weapons into our hemisphere. He says: 'To wait is to commit national suicide.'"
        },
        "intel": {
          "label": "Threat Radius",
          "image": "https://dwaugh-edsim.github.io/projectimages/cuba62/cuba-missilerange.jpg",
          "credit": "CIA THREAT PROJECTION - AI",
          "content": "### THREAT RADIUS CALCULATION\n\nThis classified map shows how far the missiles can travel. \n\n**Warning Time Analysis:**\n* **Missile from Russia:** ~25 Minutes (Detected by Radar).\n* **Missile from Cuba:** ~5 Minutes (Zero Radar Warning).\n\n**Strategic Implication:**\nIf the President is in Washington, he would have less than 5 minutes to get to a bunker. This destroys our ability to fight back. It destabilizes the balance of power overnight."
        }
